 cooley is unafraid to challenge the eternal and the certain. These poems are humorous, intelligent, and poignant. body works is essential reading for anyone who lives inside a body that lives within the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCanadian poetryy21st century. 0aEnglish poetry. 7aPOETRY / Subjects & Themes / Death, Grief, Loss.2bisacsh  aarthritis.  abiology.  abodies.  acanadian poetry.  adeath.  adying.  agout.  aheart attack.  aheart problems.  aheart.  aidentity.  aillness.  aimmunology.  amortality.  apoetry.  athe body politic.  athe body.  atime.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311127195808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP w/o University of Toronto Press 2023 eBook Packagez978311143542840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781773854502?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781773854502423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781773854502/original  a978-3-11-127195-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-143542-8  ACUP w/o University of Toronto Press 2023 eBook Packageb2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles